    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "r29",
      "x": 780,
      "y": 252,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 120,
      "backgroundColor": "#d0bfff",
      "strokeColor": "#7048e8",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t30",
      "x": 796,
      "y": 266,
      "text": "SINGLE Feed Handler\n\nDedup by (instrument, timestamp)\nWhichever source arrives first WINS\nSecond arrival = duplicate \u2192 drop\n~4K TPS in \u2192 ~2K TPS out (after dedup)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#7048e8"
    },
    {
      "type": "arrow",
      "id": "a31",
      "x": 1030,
      "y": 372,
      "width": 0,
      "height": 30,
      "strokeColor": "#7048e8",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "points": [
        [
          0,
          0
        ],
        [
          0,
          30
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "r32",
      "x": 780,
      "y": 402,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 77,
      "backgroundColor": "#d3f9d8",
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t33",
      "x": 796,
      "y": 416,
      "text": "ALL users\n\u2192 Best-of-both prices\n\u2192 Fastest available + most complete",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44"
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "r34",
      "x": 780,
      "y": 504,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 112,
      "backgroundColor": "#d3f9d8",
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t35",
      "x": 796,
      "y": 518,
      "text": "BENEFITS:\n\u2022 Every user gets fastest available price\n\u2022 NSE drops packet \u2192 Omnenest fills gap (automatic)\n\u2022 Omnenest continuously validated (every tick compared)\n\u2022 NSE dies \u2192 zero-switchover failover\n\u2022 No user is ever on the 'slower' path",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44"
    },
    {
      "type": "rectangle",
      "id": "r36",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 646,
      "width": 1320,
      "height": 102,
      "backgroundColor": "#fff9db",
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "t37",
      "x": 66,
      "y": 662,
      "text": "EXAMPLE \u2014 RELIANCE Tick Flow\n\n09:15:00.001 \u2014 NSE delivers @ \u20b92,450 \u2192 Feed Handler processes (first arrival wins)\n09:15:00.005 \u2014 Omnenest delivers same tick \u2192 skipped (duplicate by instrument+timestamp)\n09:15:00.010 \u2014 NSE misses the next tick (UDP packet loss) \u2192 Omnenest delivers 4 ms later \u2192 Feed Handler processes it (gap auto-filled, no data loss!)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00"
    }
  ],
